❌ Common Mistakes (VERY IMPORTANT)
❌ 1. Sorting ascending
sort(v.begin(), v.end()); ❌

👉 You take weakest students → WRONG

✅ Fix:

sort(v.rbegin(), v.rend());
❌ 2. Looping k outside
for(k)
   for(groups)

👉 Causes TLE

❌ 3. Forgetting prefix sum

👉 Leads to O(n²) summation

❌ 4. Using map inefficiently

Better:

vector<vector<ll>> groups(n+1);
🔥 Pattern Learned
🎯 Pattern Name:

Group + Sort + Prefix + Contribution

When to use:
Partitioning into teams/groups
Taking top k repeatedly
Sum of best elements
“Ignore leftovers” problems
